1
00:01:08,800 --> 00:01:09,460
My Lord.

2
00:01:09,760 --> 00:01:10,860
How did they know our whereabouts?

3
00:01:10,860 --> 00:01:12,630
Either they were following us all along,

4
00:01:12,630 --> 00:01:13,000
or

5
00:01:13,700 --> 00:01:14,400
someone in the Criminal Justice Department

6
00:01:14,400 --> 00:01:15,330
tipped them off.

7
00:01:17,030 --> 00:01:18,730
Check who entered or left under unusual circumstances

8
00:01:18,730 --> 00:01:19,860
from last night to this morning.

9
00:01:19,860 --> 00:01:21,390
I will go see Director Zhou.

10
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:23,289
Father once said

11
00:01:23,500 --> 00:01:24,860
Zhou Yan is an old friend.

12
00:01:24,860 --> 00:01:26,200
But seven years have passed,

13
00:01:26,200 --> 00:01:28,200
and people's hearts change easily.

14
00:01:34,660 --> 00:01:35,660
Director.

15
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:38,560
I examined a bizarre case last night.

16
00:01:38,660 --> 00:01:40,560
I found this in the crevice of the coffin.

17
00:01:40,560 --> 00:01:41,620
Please take a look.

18
00:01:41,830 --> 00:01:43,360
This is official cloud-patterned brocade,

19
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:45,630
exclusively for officials above the sixth rank to make everyday clothes.

20
00:01:45,630 --> 00:01:46,229
The worn part has

21
00:01:46,229 --> 00:01:47,600
a special soap locust smell.

22
00:01:47,600 --> 00:01:48,530
It is unique to the soap locust used by the laundry room

23
00:01:48,530 --> 00:01:49,930
inside the Criminal Justice Department.

24
00:01:49,930 --> 00:01:50,729
Are you saying

25
00:01:53,200 --> 00:01:54,300
the killer might be

26
00:01:54,300 --> 00:01:56,200
someone inside the Criminal Justice Department?

27
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:56,860
Or at least,

28
00:01:57,729 --> 00:02:00,230
someone who can easily access officials' clothes in the department,

29
00:02:00,230 --> 00:02:01,460
and carry them in and out

30
00:02:01,460 --> 00:02:03,260
without attracting attention.

31
00:02:03,600 --> 00:02:04,460
I will secretly

32
00:02:04,630 --> 00:02:06,090
investigate this matter.

33
00:02:06,560 --> 00:02:07,490
Archivist Shen,

34
00:02:07,560 --> 00:02:08,960
this case involves a lot.

35
00:02:10,229 --> 00:02:11,690
Let's put it aside for now.

36
00:02:11,960 --> 00:02:13,760
I will assign someone else to it.

37
00:02:14,460 --> 00:02:14,920
My Lord.

38
00:02:16,160 --> 00:02:17,360
I have another doubt.

39
00:02:17,500 --> 00:02:19,100
Seven years ago, why was the case file of the missing Prefect Gu Wenyuan of Yunzhou

40
00:02:19,100 --> 00:02:20,260
a blank blood letter?

41
00:02:20,260 --> 00:02:21,460
A blank blood letter?

42
00:02:29,160 --> 00:02:30,160
Old cases

43
00:02:30,530 --> 00:02:31,630
have long been sealed.

44
00:02:31,630 --> 00:02:32,260
That file

45
00:02:33,800 --> 00:02:35,700
might have become damp and mildewed.

46
00:02:35,700 --> 00:02:36,829
Will damp and mildew

47
00:02:37,530 --> 00:02:40,329
reveal seven bloody fingerprints and a prophecy?

48
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:48,600
Mo.

49
00:02:49,030 --> 00:02:50,960
I have been friends with your father for many years.

50
00:02:50,960 --> 00:02:51,829
Listen to me.

51
00:02:51,860 --> 00:02:53,860
Some cases cannot be investigated.

52
00:02:54,000 --> 00:02:54,800
For your sake,

53
00:02:55,000 --> 00:02:55,800
and for

54
00:02:55,800 --> 00:02:57,460
your father's reputation.

55
00:03:07,430 --> 00:03:09,060
I have my own plans for this case.

56
00:03:09,060 --> 00:03:09,900
Archivist Shen,

57
00:03:09,900 --> 00:03:10,760
you have been overworked recently.

58
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:11,490
Rest for now.

59
00:03:11,700 --> 00:03:15,030
You are not allowed to investigate further without orders.

60
00:03:18,600 --> 00:03:19,400
Yes.

61
00:03:23,730 --> 00:03:25,130
Uncle Zhou is warning me.

62
00:03:27,360 --> 00:03:27,820
My Lord.

63
00:03:27,930 --> 00:03:28,530
I found it.

64
00:03:28,829 --> 00:03:29,860
From last night to this morning,

65
00:03:29,860 --> 00:03:31,530
only Director's personal servant,

66
00:03:31,530 --> 00:03:31,930
Zhou Fu,

67
00:03:31,930 --> 00:03:33,000
went out late at night.

68
00:03:33,000 --> 00:03:34,530
He said he was getting medicine for the Director,

69
00:03:34,530 --> 00:03:35,900
but the direction he went

70
00:03:35,900 --> 00:03:37,100
was not the pharmacy.

71
00:03:38,660 --> 00:03:40,990
Abandoned Garden in the western suburbs.

72
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:45,000
There is indeed something suspicious.

73
00:03:45,060 --> 00:03:45,990
Prepare a horse.

74
00:03:46,030 --> 00:03:47,630
Let's go to the Abandoned Garden in the western suburbs.

75
00:03:47,630 --> 00:03:48,160
Also,

76
00:03:48,730 --> 00:03:49,260
send someone to secretly

77
00:03:49,260 --> 00:03:50,990
keep an eye on Zhou Fu's family.

78
00:03:56,100 --> 00:03:56,860
Yes, My Lord.

79
00:04:16,300 --> 00:04:17,000
Mo'er,

80
00:04:17,300 --> 00:04:18,500
you shouldn't have come.

81
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:19,160
Uncle Zhou,

82
00:04:19,660 --> 00:04:20,790
what's in this well?

83
00:04:21,630 --> 00:04:22,160
It was me.

84
00:04:22,830 --> 00:04:23,730
I did it all.

85
00:04:24,560 --> 00:04:25,660
I perverted the law,

86
00:04:25,660 --> 00:04:26,500
conspired with thieves,

87
00:04:26,500 --> 00:04:27,560
stole corpses from the mortuary,

88
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:29,100
and faked supernatural events.

89
00:04:29,100 --> 00:04:29,960
I plead guilty.

90
00:04:30,200 --> 00:04:31,130
Just arrest me.

91
00:04:33,360 --> 00:04:33,800
Uncle Zhou.

92
00:04:33,800 --> 00:04:35,500
Stealing corpses requires physical labor.

93
00:04:35,500 --> 00:04:36,560
How could you do it

94
00:04:36,560 --> 00:04:37,400
when you are old and weak?

95
00:04:37,400 --> 00:04:38,600
This brother, Zhou Fu,

96
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:39,900
went out to get medicine this morning,

97
00:04:39,900 --> 00:04:40,760
yet the soles of his shoes are stained

98
00:04:40,760 --> 00:04:42,260
with the same red soil as here.

99
00:04:42,260 --> 00:04:42,930
The person he went to see

100
00:04:42,930 --> 00:04:44,390
was probably not a doctor.

101
00:04:44,600 --> 00:04:45,730
Have mercy, My Lord.

102
00:04:47,659 --> 00:04:48,260
Someone kidnapped

103
00:04:48,260 --> 00:04:49,630
Director's young son,

104
00:04:49,630 --> 00:04:50,630
forcing him to take the blame,

105
00:04:50,630 --> 00:04:51,500
and forcing me to lead the way

106
00:04:51,500 --> 00:04:52,860
to destroy things by this well.

107
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:53,360
I...

108
00:04:53,360 --> 00:04:55,100
I was also forced.

109
00:04:56,100 --> 00:04:56,960
It's over.

110
00:04:57,600 --> 00:04:58,730
It's all over.

111
00:04:58,730 --> 00:05:00,530
Hand over the Blood Chalcedony.

112
00:05:03,200 --> 00:05:04,260
Director Zhou,

113
00:05:04,260 --> 00:05:05,360
you failed in your duty,

114
00:05:05,360 --> 00:05:06,900
and the master is very disappointed.

115
00:05:06,900 --> 00:05:08,930
Since Registrar Shen insists on seeking death,

116
00:05:08,930 --> 00:05:10,060
I'll grant your wish

117
00:05:10,130 --> 00:05:11,530
and bury you in this well.

118
00:05:15,760 --> 00:05:17,830
You led the way here to destroy things.

119
00:05:17,830 --> 00:05:18,730
Destroy what?

120
00:05:19,260 --> 00:05:20,700
They were thrown into the well.

121
00:05:20,700 --> 00:05:22,160
Then let's go down and see.

122
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:25,820
My Lord.

123
00:05:30,460 --> 00:05:31,190
Seal the well

124
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:32,659
and pour kerosene.

125
00:05:39,200 --> 00:05:40,500
Man-made.

126
00:05:40,659 --> 00:05:41,600
Not very old.

127
00:05:43,530 --> 00:05:44,860
What did you throw down?

128
00:05:44,860 --> 00:05:45,990
An oilcloth bundle.

129
00:05:46,130 --> 00:05:47,630
They said it must sink to the bottom of the well,

130
00:05:47,630 --> 00:05:49,230
the deepest part of the pool.

131
00:05:56,960 --> 00:05:57,420
My Lord.

132
00:05:57,700 --> 00:05:59,900
Tied to a stone at the bottom of the well.

133
00:06:01,460 --> 00:06:03,120
Secret underground passage.

134
00:06:03,160 --> 00:06:03,820
Array core.

135
00:06:05,130 --> 00:06:06,930
Is this token a keepsake or a key?

136
00:06:07,060 --> 00:06:09,060
Miss.

137
00:06:10,730 --> 00:06:13,160
Escape the Nine Turns.

138
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:22,200
Mural

139
00:06:23,500 --> 00:06:24,460
map.

140
00:06:32,300 --> 00:06:32,760
This map

141
00:06:33,030 --> 00:06:34,300
marks the underground secret room,

142
00:06:34,300 --> 00:06:34,830
the passage,

143
00:06:34,830 --> 00:06:35,860
and this mark.

144
00:06:36,200 --> 00:06:37,159
The core position of

145
00:06:37,159 --> 00:06:38,200
the Nine Turns Reincarnation Array.

146
00:06:38,200 --> 00:06:38,659
My Lord,

147
00:06:38,860 --> 00:06:40,159
the destiny charm in her hand.

148
00:06:40,159 --> 00:06:41,159
Jiazi,

149
00:06:41,330 --> 00:06:41,930
Yichou,

150
00:06:41,930 --> 00:06:42,600
Bingyin.

151
00:06:42,930 --> 00:06:44,130
This is my birth time.

152
00:06:44,200 --> 00:06:46,200
Why is it carved on her destiny charm?

153
00:06:46,200 --> 00:06:47,430
Is this birth character

154
00:06:47,430 --> 00:06:48,300
a coincidence,

155
00:06:48,830 --> 00:06:49,560
or...

156
00:06:52,000 --> 00:06:53,800
This dry well has a special terrain.

157
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:55,600
It's perfect for trapping them.

158
00:06:55,860 --> 00:06:57,000
Seal the well.

159
00:06:57,300 --> 00:06:58,600
Secretly send someone to keep watch.
